```{r bileducts 32590541, include=FALSE}

PMID_32590541 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32590541', database = 'PubMed')

PubMed_32590541 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32590541$eprint)

doi_32590541 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32590541$doi)
```
